What to ask your BRIDAL Mua before booking them? 

✔️ Are you available for early morning or late-night bookings?
✔️ How much time do you take to complete one makeup look?
✔️ Do you carry your own lighting or mirror setup?
✔️ Do you stay for touchups or you will provide touch up kit ?
✔️ What do you need from my side (chair, lighting, table, etc.)?
✔️ Can I request minor changes or touch-ups during the session?
✔️ what is your cancellation or refund policy 
✔️ Is there an assistant or team if I book services for multiple people?
✔️Are there any extra charges for waiting.
✔️Do you need seperate room for bride to doll her up.
